53:18.078 --> 53:22.220
added a great touch of humor
to my staged photographs.

53:22.255 --> 53:24.395
And I was very pleased
with the outcome.

53:33.680 --> 53:35.268
Sophistication.

53:36.648 --> 53:39.824
Mr. Sophistication? Of course!

53:39.858 --> 53:43.068
Your narcissism
