in your life.

57:27.534 --> 57:30.261
No, why?

57:30.295 --> 57:33.195
Well, it could be,
despite everything

57:33.229 --> 57:36.232
that speculating about this
might have triggered

57:36.267 --> 57:39.166
just a tiny bit
of human feeling.

57:39.201 --> 57:44.586
For example, a variation on
what those of us less clever

57:44.620 --> 57:46.553
might call need.

57:46.588 --> 57:49.314
Need? Because
I never had a family?

57:49.349 --> 57:52.352
No, I can't say that it did.

57:52.386 --> 57:55.873
But the concept of family
actually inspired

57:55.907 --> 57:58.289
one of my greatest works.

58:23.797 --> 58:25.661
Okay, hats for everyone

