they are seen as something

01:00:23.503 --> 01:00:27.438
of a threat to animals
you wanna cultivate.

01:00:28.819 --> 01:00:33.375
Culling, it's also such
an unpleasant word.

01:00:33.409 --> 01:00:37.482
It has a tinge of ethnic
cleansing about it.

01:00:37.517 --> 01:00:41.417
The very sick
and twisted act of hunting

01:00:41.452 --> 01:00:43.523
has been ritualized

01:00:43.557 --> 01:00:46.802
