02:10:22.019 --> 02:10:24.884
Wasn't Jack going to
build a house?

02:10:33.582 --> 02:10:34.791
Yes.

02:10:37.034 --> 02:10:40.106
I... I... I was..

02:10:44.801 --> 02:10:46.043
...trying..

